iv class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/hsJjFUCRk7k?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div id=\"v-uRqygABS-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/uRqygABS?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"21436\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1976-09-26/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1976-09-26.jpg?fit=1304%2C1647&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1304,1647\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1600596654&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1976-09-26\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1976-09-26.jpg?fit=758%2C957&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-21436 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1976-09-26.jpg?resize=758%2C957&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"957\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1976-09-26.jpg?w=1304&amp;ssl=1 1304w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1976-09-26.jpg?resize=238%2C300&amp;ssl=1 238w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1976-09-26.jpg?resize=811%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 811w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1976-09-26.jpg?resize=768%2C970&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1976-09-26.jpg?resize=1216%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 1216w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1977:\u00a0</strong>At The Power Station in New York City, Bruce holds a recording session for his upcoming album,\u00a0<em>Darkness on the Edge of Town</em>.</p>\n<p><strong>1978:\u00a0</strong>Boston DJ Mark Parenteau interviews Bruce by telephone for WBCN-FM.</p>\n<p><strong>1980:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the boys rehearse for the upcoming River Tour at Clair Brothers Audio in Lititz, Pennsylvania, and the rehearsals are captured on video.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/ypJO5gYTrIU?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"em