mp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"4563\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1984-0926/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1984-0926.jpg?fit=399%2C624&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"399,624\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;HP oj_g510n&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1984-0926\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1984-0926.jpg?fit=399%2C624&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-4563 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1984-0926.jpg?resize=399%2C624&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"399\" height=\"624\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1984-0926.jpg?w=399&amp;ssl=1 399w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/1984-0926.jpg?resize=192%2C300&amp;ssl=1 192w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 399px) 100vw, 399px\" /></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"37801\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1984-09-26/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/1984-09-26.jpg?fit=1125%2C1585&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1125,1585\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1984-09-26\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/1984-09-26.jpg?fit=727%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-37801 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/1984-09-26.jpg?resize=758%2C1068&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"1068\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/1984-09-26.jpg?w=1125&amp;ssl=1 1125w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/1984-09-26.jpg?resize=213%2C300&amp;ssl=1 213w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/1984-09-26.jpg?resize=727%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 727w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/1984-09-26.jpg?resize=768%2C1082&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/1984-09-26.jpg?resize=1090%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 1090w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1985:\u00a0</strong>The scheduled opener for the Born in the U.S.A. Tour&#8217;s final stand becomes the closing show instead when Bruce postpones this Los Angeles show to make room for a previous rescheduled show in Denver.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"21438\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1985-09-26/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1985-09-26.jpg?fit=1355%2C1648&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1355,1648\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1600597322&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1985-09-26\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1985-09-26.jpg?fit=758%2C922&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-21438 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1985-09-26.jpg?resize=758%2C922&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"922\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1985-09-26.jpg?w=1355&amp;ssl=1 1355w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1985-09-26.jpg?resize=247%2C300&amp;ssl=1 247w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1985-09-26.jpg?resize=842%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 842w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1985-09-26.jpg?resize=768%2C934&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/1985-09-26.jpg?resize=1263%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 1263w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1991:\u00a0</strong>Bruce joins Southside Johnny and The Asbury Jukes at The Stone Pony, where the show is filmed for a promotional <em>Having a Party With Southside Johnny</em> video release to support Southside&#8217;s <em>Better Days</em> album. Watch the show along with news coverage of the event below. (Bruce only appears during &#8220;It&#8217;s Been a Long Time&#8221; at the 56 minute mark, but the entire show is well worth watching.)</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/uN_88I-2HDM?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/nQQquAfM89A?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"29535\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1991-09-26a-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/1991-09-26a.jpg?fit=1104%2C1644&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1104,1644\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Ken Rosen&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1600597744&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1991-09-26a\" data-image-descript